oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Family at Walton Court
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of Robert Walton and three of his children posed in front of Walton Court in Rugby. One of his sons sits on a horse (on left), and a barn is visible behind him. The home was built in 1881 but burned down in 1988. It was later reconstructed in 2007.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Houses; Families; Horses; Trees
